            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#freilichF" start="1707.067" end="x">Marcus, Marcus. My daughter comes... "Mother, I don't hear Freilich. They called Marcus." So I say, "We are not Marcus, our last name is Freilich." "Mother, I don't know. Our father is lost. Probably the French have caught him and he too was sent away to the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>." Then they did call out for our family.</span>
        </li>
