                <span class="">Fania Freilich</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#freilichF" start="4556.271" end="x">[Here are a few incomprehensible words on the spool.] We got away from <a class="placename" href="#vothC88" type="camp">Pithiviers</a>. A year passed. My husband worked at his trade for the Germans and we had the proper papers.</span>
        </li>
